Author: intertropical
Text: hey friend, I'm so so sorry :(   if it helps, you're bingeing because you've been restricting and your body hence seriously needs the energy/nutrients. it's biological; it does not mean that you're a bad person or that you have no self-control. you don't have to punish yourself. sending you all my love.
